    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Create a Voice or Video Deep Fake Script\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to generate the text for a phishing phone call or video script for a social media video that might convince your partner to do something.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Pick a persona you'd like to write the script as. Find pieces of text that this person has written or transcripts/quotes of things this person has said.\r\n   - Celebrity\r\n      - :::details [Example: Taylor Swift]\r\n           > “It’s here. It’s yours, it’s mine, it’s ours. It’s an album I wrote alone about the whims, fantasies, heartaches, dramas and tragedies I lived out as a young woman between 18 and 20. I remember making tracklist after tracklist, obsessing over the right way to tell the story. I had to be ruthless with my choices, and I left behind some songs I am still unfailingly proud of now.”\r\n           :::\r\n   - Family member\r\n   - School staff member\r\n\r\n2. Take on a persona to create a phone call or video script for a social media video that might convince your partner to do one of the following scenarios:\r\n   - Get person to **send money**\r\n   - **Click on a link** that’s a keylogger\r\n   - **Download** a virus\r\n   - **Send on to other people** a virus or worm\r\n   \r\n3. Prompt AI Chat to make the script more effective by utilizing one or more of following tactics:\r\n   - Emotional: fear, joy, etc.\r\n   - Time-sensitive: urgency\r\n   - Social conditioning: appeal to authority\r\n\r\n\r\n**Try it out!**\r\n\r\n:::details [<i class=\"fa fa-briefcase\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Need a starting prompt?**]\r\n>Based on the following [quote/piece of writing/tweet/email/etc], generate a short [phone call/video] script that would convince someone to [click on a link/send money/download a file/forward the message to others]: [include text/quote here]\r\n:::\r\n&nbsp\r\n",
